    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> You don't intend to pass these through the Markdown parser as well, do you?\n\nLooking at the [code used in the markdown cell](https://github.com/ipython/ipython/blob/master/IPython/html/static/notebook/js/textcell.js#L247) raises some concerns about malicious HTML being executed via widget state (when the widget persistence PR is merged).  It's part of a bigger security question that I'll add it to this week's google hangout agenda.  For now I'll wait on adding markdown/HTML support here.\n"
